Introduction

Lana (Korea: 라나; Chinese: 拉娜; stylized as LANA) is a Russian singer-songwriter, rapper, model and TV Personality under Bates MeThinks Entertainment and WILD Entertainment.

She made her Korean debut on June 27, 2019 with the single "Take The Wheel", marking her debut as the first Russian to debut as a solo k-pop artist under HiCC Entertainment.

On December 10, 2019 she released her second digital single "Make It Real", which is a surprise gift for her fandom and everyone that had been supporting her.

On March 11, 2020 she revealed that she would became a contestant on the Chinese reality survival show, Produce Camp 2020, under Bates MeThinks Entertainment.
